"reviewcomment":"I can&#39;t believe we&#39;re reviewing a mcdonalds, but this place is fantastic!  Like others have said this place is classy. They have a great café with excellent coffee, cakes, muffins, etc.  It&#39;s really high quality stuff you&#39;d expect from a bakery.  Now on to the food. Why the hell do the burgers taste so good here compared to North America?  My god, they were so fresh and tasty, the complete opposite of the slop we get here.  It actually tastes like beef.  They even give you real white napkins, not the recycled brown cardboard looking monstrosities they give here.  I know, relax, its only napkins, but it&#39;s a simple luxury that adds to the dining experience.  <br><br>We&#39;re actually embarrassed by how much we loved this place and how often we ate here, but it was too damn good.  Another reason to sell all of our possessions and move to Spain.",
