"reviewcomment":"Cheap and delicious! Cheap and delicious! I was recommended 100 Montaditos from several friends who have lived in Madrid and LOVED it! Mini sandwiches all for 1 EURO!?!?! Yes, please. We had an incredibly cheap and yummy meal at this location. I wish they had this kind of restaurant in my hometown because I would be there all the time. If you sit outside watch out for the birds; they swarm dishes left over from patrons who have left (it&#39;s a little terrifying to be enjoying your meal when all of a sudden a flock of birds flies right at the table next to you but if I was a bird I would want to eat here too). All of the montaditos (mini sandwiches) come with chips and there are so many different choices! We sampled the jamon york y queso, jamon iberico, hamburguesa and patatas fritas con 4 salsas (dipping sauces). All yum! <br><br>Step 1 Check out the menu<br>Step 2 Write your order down<br>Step 3 Bring your ticket order inside (if you&#39;re sitting outside)<br>Step 4 Wait while it is being prepared<br>Step 5 Go back in to retrieve your yummy meal<br>Step 6 Enjoy!",
