"rating":"2.5",
"reviewcomment":"A  place with high potential to bump into a celebrity. They told me before. I didn&#39;t believe. Not that I care about a celeb but if it is Sean Penn, let&#39;s hold on there for a sec. And yes I was lucky enough to meet  him and he was sharing the table with Javier Bardem, Penelope Cruz and a big group of people. It was a surrealistic experience until the idiot waiter brought me back to the lame reality running towards me like a baseball player going for touchdown.<br><br>Well food! Sorry but I haven&#39;t eaten anything here :) but only joined my friends who were dining that night.  However, there were quiet satisfied with everything and I can assure you those girls have good taste in food. <br><br>On the other hand, it is a posh restaurant bar and therefore not my cup of tea. So depends on the person and what you like. On the first floor there was a DJ and many girls on high heels. You can picture better now right? So again it is your call whether you go or not.",
