"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"This is one of three locations for this restaurant, my comment below is almost identical to the one I wrote for Lupita II.<br><br>The service is not great (but certainly better than their Gran Via location) but the portion sizes and the food certainly more than make up for it. The portions are enormous! So be careful when ordering, you might just order double what you can eat. Although, it&#39;s not really a big problem because you can just ask to take it to go, they have no problem giving you take out boxes. The chicken is their most ordered dish and it is delicious! It comes with a side of salad, french fries and two delicious spicy sauces. A large group could eat here very cheaply. All the dishes i&#39;ve tried here have been great, from the appetizers to the desserts. Sometimes we just sneak in to have one of their huge portions of chocolate cake. It is rich and always cures my sugar cravings. They have all kinds of cakes and pies, they vary depending on the day and on the time of day. If you can get over their lack of customer service you will certainly be a very happy diner here.<br><br>I forgot to mention they have delicious smoothies, try one!",
